A [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].

This pool pays out using a proportional share reward system (your shares / total shares for the round) = % share of the rewards.

The service was first available on June 28, 2011.

##Reward distribution

* Pay per share: 4% fee

## Features

* idle worker email notification
* automatic payout once a day, if amount > 1 BTC
* native patched bitcoind longpolling ( 15-20sec faster then BTCguild => fewer stales )
* live stats updates

